title: Cahors Sunset-OUTLAWS
description:
Cahors Sunset-OUTLAWS

Extract 7zip, install with exe & play!


In Cahors Sunset you control the decisions of an old French man who was born and has always lived in the city of Cahors, France. In this game your goal is try to keep the main character alive for as long as you can through actions which are beneficial for him. However, every action has a reaction, not all choices are utterly good for your character and most of them contain unwanted side effects. The point of the game is to balance the positive and negative effects of each action and the impact they have on the health of the old man.
